  "title": "自主评分的间隔重复记忆系统比机器评分的系统更有效率",
  "image_width": 1033,
  "content": "<p data-pid=\"_gf81DDN\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z87TFgTr98bz3MNFT26NhegyRCMgdkfNTBAzp\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">交互是界面设计的成本中心</a><sup data-text=\"交互是界面设计中的成本中心\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/472770296\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>，所以机器评分的<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z4eXdSMJFv2qVGXSUEKH4vdcHBrLHcFY1ZGfC\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">间隔重复记忆系统</a><sup data-text=\"间隔重复记忆系统\" data-url=\"http://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/404257681\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"2\">[2]</sup>给他们的用户带来了更大的成本。如果要求用户打字输入答案，那就很容易在每项任务上花费 2-4 倍的时间。</p><p data-pid=\"qgyyNWN_\">一些机器评分系统放弃卡片，转而使用选择题来规避输入成本。但生成任务就转变成了判别任务——对记忆编码的效果大打折扣；参见<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z3iJVoXtJBUJHq9Tb6i8Kv4EK7oNbriHh4N2y\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">生成效应</a><sup data-text=\"生成效应\" data-url=\"http://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/455748242\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"3\">[3]</sup></p><h2>链接至本文（已汉化）</h2><ul><li data-pid=\"0LQNUtIr\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/469542171\" class=\"internal\">助记媒介依赖的卡片应是轻量级的</a></li><li data-pid=\"w7wRGk62\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/573838070\" class=\"internal\">迁移恰当加工</a></li></ul><h2>声明</h2><p data-pid=\"EXe-X8pe\">此内容发布由 Andy Matuschak 许可。未经允许，不得转载或修改。保留所有权利。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"6EW3hVGB\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z7MGZ4wX4fenUQzR9248QfWU8GFeZbTFGaJRM\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Self-graded spaced repetition memory systems are more efficient than machine-graded systems (andymatuschak.org)</a></blockquote>",
